13:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both NightCafe and Pixlr AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Image To Image, Upscaling, Commercial License. Where NightCafe pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Style Transfer and Batch Generation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Pixlr AI uniquely offers Inpainting and Outpainting, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, NightCafe holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Pixlr AI scores 5/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both NightCafe and Pixlr AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. NightCafe's free tier and Pixlr AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
